        "@value": "The NSO at The Pavilion"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Bradley Thachuk, conductor\r\n\r\nMendelssohn | The Hebrides, op. 26 (“Fingal’s Cave”)\r\nMozart | Symphony No. 35, K. 385, D major (“Haffner”)\r\nBeethoven | Symphony No. 7, op. 92, A major\r\n\r\nThe NSO performs Beethoven, Mozart, and Mendelssohn at this FREE outdoor concert, held at The Pavilion at St. George Orthodox Church"
      }
    ],
