        "@value": "All Tchaikovsky - Niagara Symphony"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "Bradley Thachuk, conductor David Fung, piano Tchaikovsky | Piano Concerto No. 1 Tchaikovsky | Romeo & Juliet Tchaikovsky | 1812 Overture  The boom of war cannons and the tragedy of forbidden love – Tchaikovsky captures the passion and pain of history in his beloved scores."
      }
    ],
