      {
        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "In accordance with provincial regulations Invisible Cities featuring TorQ Percussion Quartet is postponed. All ticket holders will be contacted by the PAC box office directly with options shortly.  We remain committed to rescheduling this fantastic concert for later in the 2021-22 season with a new date to be announced as soon as possible."
