    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Symphonie fantastique"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Symphonie fantastique - our stupendous season finale!\r\n\r\n\r\nJoin us for a concert that will ignite your senses and transport you to worlds both familiar and unknown.\r\n\r\n\r\nFeel the heat of Saint-Saëns' Bacchanale from Samson et Dalila. Witness Dalila's intoxicating dance, a whirlwind of passion and provocation, as the orchestra unleashes a torrent of exotic rhythms and sensual melodies.\r\n\r\n\r\nBe captivated by the mesmerizing sounds of the tabla, brought to life by the extraordinary Gabriel Dionne. Experience the instrument's ancient tradition and its vibrant contemporary voice, as it seamlessly blends with the orchestra in Dinuk Wijeratne's innovative Tabla Concerto. Then, surrender to the intoxicating power of Berlioz's Symphonie fantastique. Let the music sweep you away on a journey of love, obsession, and fantastical visions. Feel the raw emotion and revolutionary spirit of this iconic masterpiece, a symphony that redefined the boundaries of orchestral expression. This is a season finale that will challenge your expectations and leave you breathless. \r\n\r\n\r\nFeaturing Gabriel Dionne, tabla.\r\n\r\n\r\nJoin us for a concert that will ignite your senses and transport you to worlds both familiar and unknown."
      }
    ],
