      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Experience an Afternoon of Sonic Wonder! \r\n\r\nStep into a world where time bends, melodies soar, and the past meets the future in an electrifying afternoon of music!\r\n\r\nThe concert opens with Jordan Nobles’ Coriolis-a mesmerizing, atmospheric soundscape that blurs the boundaries of space and motion, immersing you in a shimmering whirl of tone and texture.\r\n\r\nNext, journey back to the elegance of the Classical era with Mozart’s Flute Concerto No. 1-a dazzling display of virtuosity and charm, featuring graceful melodies that dance effortlessly through the air.\r\n\r\nThe night comes to a height with the majestic Symphony No. 38 “Prague”, one of Mozart’s most dramatic and thrilling symphonic works, brimming with bold contrasts and an emotional intensity that still stuns audiences today.\r\n\r\nModern sound. Classical brilliance. One unforgettable afternoon.\r\nDon't miss this extraordinary musical voyage!"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventAttendanceMode": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventStatus": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/EventScheduled"
      }
    ]
  },
