        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Holiday Magic: A Festive Celebration! \r\n\r\nJoin us for a heartwarming holiday concert filled with all your favorite carols, performed by a full orchestra and choir in a sparkling seasonal spectacular!\r\n\r\nSing along to timeless classics, feel the joy of live music, and don’t miss a special visit from Santa Claus himself - perfect for the whole family!\r\n\r\nMusic, magic, and holiday cheer - come make memories that will last all year!"
      }
