        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "article"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "Home for the Holidays - Niagara Symphony"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "Holiday Magic for the Whole Family  Celebrate the season with Niagara’s favourite holiday tradition.  Vocal Soloists Chris Blem and Stephanie Park return with festive classics, joyful sing-alongs, along with sparkling orchestral music and heartwarming surprises. Home for the Holidays is the perfect way to share the spirit of the season with family and friends.  And yes—Santa may make a special appearance!  Make memories, celebrate together, and experience the magic of the holidays through music."
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#url": [
