    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Home for the Holidays"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Holiday Magic for the Whole Family\r\n\r\nCelebrate the season with Niagara’s favourite holiday tradition.\r\n\r\nVocal Soloists Chris Blem and Stephanie Park return with festive classics, joyful sing-alongs, along with sparkling orchestral music and heartwarming surprises. Home for the Holidays is the perfect way to share the spirit of the season with family and friends.\r\n\r\nAnd yes—Santa may make a special appearance!\r\n\r\nMake memories, celebrate together, and experience the magic of the holidays through music."
      }
    ],
